      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure. This beauty is in absolute showroom condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage its whole life and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love with it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
