    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a whisper-quiet VANOS unit. Mechanically peerless, the chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. Power is managed via a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission and delivered through a tight M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with all-new OEM bushings, ensuring zero tramlining or NVH issues. A turn-key specimen for the collector demanding mechanical perfection and visceral throttle response.",
      "price": 48500.0,
