    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available now is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous Obsidian Black with a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a mirror-like finish; there are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, featuring premium Nappa leather upholstery that retains its original matte finish and factory-fresh scent. All interior electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a complete paper trail of every oil change and inspection. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with seamless precision, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or leaks. This car comes with two original keys, the full set of owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand. It is, quite simply, the finest example of this model currently on the market.",
